Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,100)\bord0\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\c&H72756F&\frz17.2\pos(722,700)}{Potential kill count: 150,000+}Ước lượng giết\N hơn 150 nghìn
